title.narrative: TPC: INL/WHP Caribbean Program Advisor. Other Services - Contract Advisory and Assistance Service Management and Professional Support Services. Information has been Redacted in accordance with the two principled exceptions of the Foreign Aid Transparency and Accountability Act (FATAA) of 2016; including the health and security of implementing partners, as well as national interest of the United States.

description.narrative: BPA Call modification to exercise Option Year 01 with a new period of performance of 09/26/2019 to 09/25/2020 for $156,484.20 for the services of a Caribbean Program Advisor supporting INL/WHP in Washington, DC.. Management and professional support services generally aim at improving the efficiency or effectiveness of management or administrative systems and normally take the form of information, opinion, advice, training or direct assistance. Contracts may be with firms or individuals.. BPA Call modification to exercise Option Year (OY) 02 with a new POP of 09/26/2020 through 09/25/2021 in the amount of $160,015.00 for the services of a Caribbean Program Advisor supporting INL/WHP in Washington, DC.. Information has been redacted in accordance with the two principled exceptions defined in the Foreign Aid Transparency and Accountability Act (FATAA) of 2016: the health and security of implementing partners, and the national interest of the United States..
